@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container my-5">

    <!-- Privacy Policy Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-5">
        <h2 class="fw-bold" style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #1E88E5;">Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #757575;">
            Your privacy is important to us. This policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information within the Contract Monthly Claim System (CMCS).
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Content Section -->
    <div class="card shadow-lg" style="border-radius: 15px; background-color: #F9F9F9;">
        <div class="card-body p-5">

            <h5 class="fw-bold mb-3" style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #1E88E5;">1. Information We Collect</h5>
            <p style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #616161;">
                When using the CMCS, we may collect the following information:
            </p>
            <ul style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #616161;">
                <li><strong>Personal Identification Information:</strong> Name, email address, contact information, etc.</li>
                <li><strong>Employment Information:</strong> Hours worked, hourly rate, submitted claims, etc.</li>
                <li><strong>Supporting Documents:</strong> Any files uploaded in relation to your claims.</li>
            </ul>

            <h5 class="fw-bold mb-3 mt-4" style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #1E88E5;">2. How We Use Your Information</h5>
            <p style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #616161;">
                The information collected is used to process, review, and approve your claims efficiently. We also use this data to:
            </p>
            <ul style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #616161;">
                <li>Verify your work hours and payments.</li>
                <li>Generate accurate monthly claims.</li>
                <li>Improve the functionality and user experience of the system.</li>
            </ul>

            <h5 class="fw-bold mb-3 mt-4" style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #1E88E5;">3. Information Sharing and Disclosure</h5>
            <p style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #616161;">
                Your data is confidential. It will only be shared with:
            </p>
            <ul style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #616161;">
                <li><strong>Programme Coordinators and Academic Managers:</strong> for claim approval.</li>
                <li><strong>Internal Administrative Personnel:</strong> for administrative purposes.</li>
                <li>We will not share your data with third parties without your consent, except where required by law.</li>
            </ul>

            <h5 class="fw-bold mb-3 mt-4" style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #1E88E5;">4. Data Security</h5>
            <p style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #616161;">
                We take your data security seriously. Measures are in place to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure.
            </p>

            <h5 class="fw-bold mb-3 mt-4" style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #1E88E5;">5. Your Rights</h5>
            <p style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #616161;">
                You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal data at any time. You can request a copy of your data or ask for corrections if needed.
            </p>

            <h5 class="fw-bold mb-3 mt-4" style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #1E88E5;">6. Changes to This Policy</h5>
            <p style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #616161;">
                We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with a revised date.
            </p>

            <h5 class="fw-bold mb-3 mt-4" style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #1E88E5;">7. Contact Us</h5>
            <p style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #616161;">
                If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please contact us at
                <a href="mailto:support@cmcs-system.com" style="color: #1E88E5; text-decoration: none;">support@cmcs-system.com</a>.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

